\fs36 \cf0 How Every Referral Gets Tracked, Attributed, and Paid\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \strokec0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 The Short Answer\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Every pro in the network gets three things the moment they are activated:\
1.A unique referral link \'97 shareable digitally (text, email, social, DM)\
2.A unique QR code \'97 printable on physical materials\
3.A printed starter kit \'97 mailed to their business address within 5 business days of activation\
All three point to the same tracking record in the database. It does not matter which one a new pro uses to sign up \'97 the attribution is identical.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \strokec0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 How the Referral Link Works\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Each pro's referral link follows this format:\
Plain Text\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2 \cf0 \strokec2 https://prolnk.io/join?ref=XXXXXX\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1 \cf0 \strokec2 Where XXXXXX is a unique 6-character alphanumeric code assigned to each pro at account creation. This code is stored in the database and permanently tied to that pro's account.\
When a new pro clicks the link and completes enrollment:\
\'95The ref parameter is captured on landing\
\'95It is stored in a browser cookie (30-day expiration ) and in the URL session\
\'95When the new pro submits their application, the referring pro's ID is written to the new pro's record in the referred_by field\
\'95The system then walks up the tree to assign L1, L2, L3, and L4 relationships automatically\
The referral link is the primary digital tool. It is what a pro sends via text message, posts in a Facebook group, or drops in a group chat.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \strokec0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 How the QR Code Works\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Each pro's QR code encodes the exact same URL as their referral link:\
Plain Text\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2 \cf0 \strokec2 https://prolnk.io/join?ref=XXXXXX\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1 \cf0 \strokec2 The QR code is generated automatically at account creation and is available for download from the pro's dashboard at any time. It is also pre-printed on all physical materials.\
When someone scans the QR code with their phone, it opens the enrollment page with the referring pro's code already embedded \'97 same tracking logic as the digital link.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \strokec0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

