\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 The Full Tracking Stack\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Plain Text\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2 \cf0 \strokec2 New pro signs up \uc0\u9474  \u9500 \u9472 \u9472  Via referral link (digital) \u9474  \u9492 \u9472 \u9472  ref= parameter captured \u8594  stored in cookie + session \u9474  \u9500 \u9472 \u9472  Via QR code scan (physical) \u9474  \u9492 \u9472 \u9472  Same ref= parameter \u8594  same tracking logic \u9474  \u9492 \u9472 \u9472  Via direct enrollment (no referral) \u9492 \u9472 \u9472  ref= is null \u8594  assigned to general pool, no upline \u8595  Enrollment form submitted \u9474  \u9492 \u9472 \u9472  referred_by field written to new pro's DB record \u9492 \u9472 \u9472  System walks tree: who referred the referrer? (up to 4 levels) \u9492 \u9472 \u9472  L1, L2, L3, L4 relationships stored in network_relationships table \u8595  Pro activates (subscription confirmed) \u9474  \u9492 \u9472 \u9472  Unique referral link generated (ref code) \u9492 \u9472 \u9472  QR code generated and stored \u9492 \u9472 \u9472  Print-and-mail job triggered \u8594  starter kit ships to business address \u9492 \u9472 \u9472  Dashboard unlocked \u8594  pro can see their referral link + QR code \u8595  Pro closes a job \u9474  \u9492 \u9472 \u9472  Job value recorded \u9492 \u9472 \u9472  Commission engine runs: - Pro earns their own-job rate - L1 above them earns 2% of job value - L2 above them earns 1.5% of job value - L3 above them earns 1.0% of job value - L4 above them earns 0.5% of job value \u9492 \u9472 \u9472  All payouts queued for end-of-month disbursement\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1 \cf0 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
